[48;2;79;40;40m[39m- 236     [0m:[39m[48;2;36;25;28m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mReal-time path.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m For dispense events that can be held briefly for screening (order verification, cabinet pull at the dispensing point), the pipeline runs a rule-based check followed by a population-level z-score against the drug-class-specific distribution for similar patients. The latency budget is on the order of tens to low hundreds of milliseconds end-to-end. The output is a severity tier that drives the UX: interrupt the pharmacist synchronously, add to a review queue, or log for background analysis.[K
